Package org.openhab.binding.velux.internal

Classes for handling of openHAB bindings and configurations.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    VeluxBinding
    Class for Velux binding which validates the bridge configuration parameters.
    VeluxBindingConfig
    This represents the configuration of a openHAB item that is binded to a Velux KLF200 Gateway.
    VeluxBindingConstants
    The VeluxBindingConstants class defines common constants, which are used across the whole binding.
    VeluxBindingProperties
    The VeluxBindingProperties class defines common constants, which are used within the property definitions.
    VeluxRSBindingConfig
    This represents the configuration of a openHAB item that is binded to a Velux KLF200 Gateway.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description

    Enumeration of Types of a Velux item.
